name: Hide and Seek Watercolor
description: This original watercolor painting was done in preparation for another project. It features a cool puppy guy and a kitten gal who are playing hide and seek. It kinda looks like the cat is winning. This 7x9 inches piece of artwork was completed in watercolor and watercolor pencils on Strathmore coldpress watercolor paper.

name: Original 5"x7" Ink Drawings
description:
For only $10, I'll do a nice little ink sketch on high quality paper and ship it to you! You can just let me draw whatever comes to my mind or pick the topic (almost ANY topic or subject within reason!) and I draw an original ink drawing of that topic or subject. It is best to keep it simple though. The drawing won't be super complicated since it is a little sketch, but I will give it care and love as to make sure you'll enjoy it!
Just give me a simple one-word type of description for me to use as a place to start. 
(However, I won't draw anything that's inappropriate or "PG-13 and up." I do prefer not to do drawings of you, your family, or friends because those require a bit more care  and time than this price allows.)

For the drawing shown here, the suggestion was, "Jimmy Olson."

These original pieces of artwork make great gifts for friends, family, or yourself!

Shoot me an idea or just ask for a sketch of anything and I will draw it up, ink it, and send it your way!

name: Original 8"x10" ink drawings
description:
For just $25, I'll do a nice drawing on high quality Bristol board paper and ship it to you! You pick the topic (almost ANY topic or subject within reason!) and I draw an original ink drawing of that topic or subject. It can be a character, animal, idea, or whatever! It is up to you! 
Just give me a simple one-word type of description for me to use as a place to start. (However, I won't draw anything that's inappropriate or "PG-13 and up." I do prefer not to do drawings of you, your family, or friends because those require a bit more care  and time than this price allows.)

These original pieces of artwork make great gifts for friends, family, or yourself!

Shoot me an idea and I will draw it up, ink it, and send it your way!

The ink drawing shown in this photo had the subject, "Little Nemo meets Miyazaki." I was for a friend, so I spent a bit more time on it and was OK with it being more complicated. Some drawings maybe a bit simpler, but I'm pretty sure you'll dig them!
